ax-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"1220\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-1-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1220\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-1-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2024/08/NTWP-2024-08-1.jpg 957w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" /></a></figure>\n<figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\"><strong>Hình ảnh sự kiện Nha Trang WordPress Meetup 25/08/2024</strong></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/2b50.png\" alt=\"⭐\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Nha Trang WordPress Meetup 25/08/2024 <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/2b50.png\" alt=\"⭐\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f3af.png\" alt=\"🎯\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> <strong>Thời gian tổ chức: </strong>08h30 ngày 25/08/2024</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f3af.png\" alt=\"🎯\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Địa điểm:</strong> Stockholm Bistro &amp; Co-working</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">43 Lý Tự Trọng, Thành phố Nha Trang, Khánh Hoà</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f4a5.png\" alt=\"💥\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Chủ đề 1: Quy trình xử lý mã độc chuyên nghiệp cho website WordPress</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Speaker: Nguyễn Xuân Bình Minh &#8211; CEO Minh Duy Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f4a5.png\" alt=\"💥\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Chủ đề 2: Bí quyết x10 doanh số với chiến lược phễu bán hàng trong WordPress</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Speaker: Nguyễn Minh Phụng &#8211; CEO Công ty TNHH Giải Pháp ETI</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f4a5.png\" alt=\"💥\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Chủ đề 3: 5 Ways to increase your Businesses Profits</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Speaker: Hà Anh Lĩnh &#8211; CEO Công ty TNHH TM &amp; DV ANHLINHMKT</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f3af.png\" alt=\"🎯\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Phí tham dự:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">&#8211; Miễn phí tham dự</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">&#8211; Số lượng tối đa: 30 người</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f3af.png\" alt=\"🎯\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Đơn vị tài trợ chính:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/2b50.png\" alt=\"⭐\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Công ty TNHH Xây Dựng &amp; Công Nghệ Quỳnh An (Quỳnh An Solar)</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/2b50.png\" alt=\"⭐\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> CÔNG TY CỔ PHẦN FUTE (Web2M &amp; Pay2S)</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/72x72/1f3af.png\" alt=\"🎯\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Đơn vị tổ chức: Minh Duy Solutions &amp; Minh Duy Event</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"></figure>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2024/08/25/hinh-anh-su-kien-nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-25-08-2024/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"1175\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"Đăng ký tham dự Nha Trang WordPress Meetup 25/08/2024\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2024/08/09/dang-ky-tham-du-nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-25-08-2024/\";s:7:\"attribs\";