 -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#\">XEM THÊM</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9 size-full\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"bottom\":\"0px\",\"top\":\"144px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"inherit\":false,\"contentSize\":\"1200px\",\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" id=\"services\" style=\"padding-top:144px;padding-bottom:0px\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dịch vụ</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"50px\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\" style=\"margin-top:50px\"><!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"8px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":40,\"width\":\"357px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"aspectRatio\":\"0.7490627571702887\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-40\" style=\"aspect-ratio:0.7490627571702887;width:357px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"16px\"}}}} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-top:16px\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-ast-global-color-0-color\">Cập nhật</mark></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bản cập nhật Tốc Chiến 7.1b (ra mắt 15/04/2026) đánh dấu sự xuất hiện của Đấu Sĩ K\'Sante với khả năng chuyển đổi trạng thái chiến đấu linh hoạt.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"8px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":41,\"width\":\"384px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-41\" style=\"width:384px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"16px\"}}}} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-top:16px\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-ast-global-color-0-color\">Sự kiện</mark></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong thời gian này, game cũng tung ra nhiều sự kiện hấp dẫn, nổi bật là màn hợp tác với hãng xe Porsche và sự kiện Võ Đài Tối Thượng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"8px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":42,\"width\":\"384px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"aspectRatio\":\"0.5600156138182292\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-42\" style=\"aspect-ratio:0.5600156138182292;width:384px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"16px\"}}}} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-top:16px\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-ast-global-color-0-color\">Tin tức</mark></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mùa giải Xếp hạng 21 đã chính thức khởi tranh cùng hệ thống tính điểm được tối ưu hóa. Người chơi tham gia leo rank trong mùa này sẽ có cơ hội nhận được phần thưởng trang phục độc quyền là Jax Vinh Quang.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"143px\",\"bottom\":\"144px\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"ast-global-color-5\",\"layout\":{\"inherit\":false,\"contentSize\":\"1200px\",\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-ast-global-color-5-background-color has-background\" id=\"about\" style=\"padding-top:143px;padding-bottom:144px\"><!-- wp:media-text {\"align\":\"\",\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":43,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/tocchien/trang-chu/1-2/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":56,\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 56%\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"80px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"inherit\":true,\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"padding-right:80px\"><!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"40px\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"padding-right:40px\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#ff6900\" class=\"has-inline-color\">VNG</mark></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#ff6900\" class=\"has-inline-color\">VNG Corporation</mark></strong> tiền thân là Vinagame được thành lập vào năm 2004 và là một trong những tập đoàn công nghệ lớn nhất tại Việt Nam. Đây cũng là doanh nghiệp khởi nghiệp đầu tiên của Việt Nam đạt mức định giá trên 1 tỷ USD, chính thức trở thành \"kỳ lân công nghệ\" đầu tiên của đất nước.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-43 size-full\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"backgroundColor\":\"ast-global-color-4\",\"layout\":{\"inherit\":false,\"contentSize\":\"800px\",\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-ast-global-color-4-background-color has-background\" id=\"reviews\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":235,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/themes/astra/inc/assets/images/starter-content/avatar.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-235\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><p class=\"”has-text-align-center\" has-ast-global-color-2-color=\"\" has-text-color”=\"\" style=\"”font-size:22px;line-height:1.6”\">”The best part is that Astra comes with hundreds of professionally designed templates for just about every industry, makes it super easy for non-techy users to build a website.”</p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"ast-global-color-2\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-ast-global-color-2-color has-text-color\"><strong>Wade Warren</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"144px\",\"bottom\":\"144px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"inherit\":false,\"contentSize\":\"1200px\",\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" id=\"whyus\" style=\"padding-top:144px;padding-bottom:144px\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Choose Us</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"80px\",\"margin\":{\"top\":\"60px\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\" style=\"margin-top:60px\"><!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"8px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":162,\"width\":48,\"height\":48,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/themes/astra/inc/assets/images/starter-content/passionate.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-162\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"16px\"}}}} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-top:16px\">Passionate</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tempor ullamcorper urna, est, lectus amet sit tempor pretium mi sed morbi cras posuere sit ultrices bibendum augue sit ornare.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"8px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":163,\"width\":48,\"height\":48,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/themes/astra/inc/assets/images/starter-content/professional.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-163\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"16px\"}}}} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-top:16px\">Professional</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tempor ullamcorper urna, est, lectus amet sit tempor pretium mi sed morbi cras posuere sit ultrices bibendum augue sit ornare.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"8px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":164,\"width\":48,\"height\":48,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/tocchien/wp-content/themes/astra/inc/assets/images/starter-content/support.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-164\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"16px\"}}}} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-top:16px\">Support</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tempor ullamcorper urna, est, lectus amet sit tempor pretium mi sed morbi cras posuere sit ultrices bibendum augue sit ornare.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"gradient\":\"linear-gradient(35deg,rgb(6,0,151) 0%,rgb(130,4,255) 64%,rgb(193,15,255) 98%)\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"104px\",\"bottom\":\"104px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"inherit\":false,\"contentSize\":\"520px\",\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background\" id=\"contact\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(35deg,rgb(6,0,151) 0%,rgb(130,4,255) 64%,rgb(193,15,255) 98%);padding-top:104px;padding-bottom:104px\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffffff\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffffff\">Get a professional website today!</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"50px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\",\"orientation\":\"horizontal\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignwide\" style=\"margin-top:50px\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\">XEM THÊM</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'Trang chủ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2026-04-19 07:16:02', '2026-04-19 07:16:02', '', 11, 'http://localhost/tocchien/?p=45', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
